_sText:
Hi, sorry for the delay till my last map :P Didnt have inspiration...

This is a obstacle map, i think it has 18 or 17 levels :P Dont remember how many XD

You have to beat all the obstacles without dying, some levels dont hurt tho.
In the end if you finish first your colour will change and you can pick a weapon up and then restart.

All levels are makeable i have checked and hopefully u like this map as it brings something new to obstacle maps, such as hoostie boost or smoke blocking.
Theres 2 possible labirynths and it spawns randomly so you dont end up knowing the way so easily like in most obstacle maps.
Thers a random hurt system and the "Try your luck" obstacle

Have fun, Borixon
